{"tid":1061294,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【三個夠晒數】被批越多女人越有財富 鄧兆尊：呢句嘢可以判死刑","createTime":"2019-03-14T10:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T23:33:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6e71371a9ad7b8818ec3b33180a16a7050132deb","tid":1061294,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:01:36.000Z","msg":"鄧兆尊昨晚在九龍灣為ViuTV玄學節目《點相》擔任嘉賓，他透露在節目中，皓云師傅批他越多女人就越有財富：「我一聽到，即刻面青，呢句嘢可以判死刑。」兆尊表示更獲師傅提醒他將會有個小劫，他說：「我60幾歲嘅時候係有個小劫，我自己都知，我估係健康，冇乜大問題嘅。」會否每年驗身？他直言會被迫去驗。<br />\n再問有否叫師傅看他有沒有子女緣？兆尊即笑說：「冇講喎，係喎，應該問吓呢個問題喎，如果佢話有，我點算？會好煩㗎，你知我有幾個已經『收咗工』，講笑啫，呢啲隨緣啦！」此外，對於有報道指兆尊的家族西貢地向城規會申請改劃，他解釋：「我細佬（兆榮）聽朋友講，試吓規劃咗先，將來做買賣會好啲，既然佢做咗就由佢去做，其實無傷大雅。」會否打算發展？他即說：「冇，嗰度咁多蚊，而且好偏僻。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190314/large/1552550698_b6de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190314%2Flarge%2F1552550698_b6de.jpg&h=f0baa2fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190314/large/1552550698_0a37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190314%2Flarge%2F1552550698_0a37.jpg&h=8a90832d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190314/large/1552550698_9727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190314%2Flarge%2F1552550698_9727.jpg&h=52ac5fe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41cc7dd680e41146cee02cf6cb1090bed89d8c96","tid":1061294,"uid":52122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"佢係未覺得自己係洗米華？"},{"pid":"bebf870da08410b92e9b461c20b8b008296b0ebc","tid":1061294,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T21:43:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f484fc5332f5b82aee896f89555a65fbee99bd8","tid":1061294,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p